Package com.habelitz.jsobjectizer.jsom.api.statement

Interface Summary
AssertStatement This Statement type represents an assert statement.
BreakStatement This Statement type represents a break statement.
ContinueStatement This Statement type represents a continue statement.
ExpressionStatement This Statement type represents an expression on statement level.
ForEachStatement This Statement type represents an for statement that matches the forEach syntax.
ForStatement This Statement type represents a for statement.
IfStatement This Statement type represents an if statement.
LabeledStatement This Statement type represents a labeled statement.
LocalClassDeclaration This StatementBlockElement type represents a local class declaration.
LocalVariableDeclaration This StatementBlockElement type represents a local variable declaration.
ReturnStatement This Statement type represents a return statement.
Statement This StatementBlockElement type represents all kinds of statements.
StatementBlockElement This JSOM type represents a statement block element.
StatementBlockScope This Statement type represents a statement block scope, i.e. a method body, a compound statement and so on.
SwitchStatement This Statement type represents a switch statement.
SwitchStatement.SwitchLabel Represents case and default clauses.
SynchronizedStatement This Statement type represents a synchronized statement.
ThrowStatement This Statement type represents a throw statement.
TryStatement This Statement type represents a try statement.
TryStatement.Catch Represents catch clauses.
WhileAndDoStatements This Statement type represents either a while or a do...while statement.
 

Enum Summary
ForStatement.ForInitType Defines constants for the various types of for statement initializers.
StatementBlockElement.ElementType Defines constants for each statement block element type.
StatementBlockScope.Owner Defines constants for all possible owners of a statement block scope.
